13. Plush Headplay Evil Bad Banana Man 
The stuff of my nightmares right here. However this little deviant banana man would be a hilarious gift for that one coworker whose desk needs a little spicing up. 14 
14. Fake Breast Squeeze Ball 
So we actually have these booby-licious stress balls at our office and they’re AMAZING. You don’t even realize how therapeutic they are until you give them a nice squeeze. Plus, they’re a great way to troll coworkers.
